  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nWould be very cool to be able to call \r\n```sh\r\nforge install git@github.com:foundry-rs/foundry.git\r\n```\r\nand to have in .gitmodules SSH integration, not HTTPS. Currently [HTTPS forced](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/65a37e4f6d1b529a403ba8c2a3d68474aefec897/cli/src/opts/forge.rs#L258).\r\n\r\nIt helps when working with private modules. You don't need to pass an access token or login/password every time.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
